  "prompt": "How many grafts are needed to get a full beard by facial hair transplant? How much will it cost in India?",
  "response": "The number of grafts needed for a full beard transplant can vary significantly based on individual factors such as the density of the desired beard, the size of the area to be covered, and the natural hair growth characteristics of the individual. On average, a full beard transplant may require anywhere from 1000 to 3000 grafts. \n\nAs for the cost of a beard transplant in India, it typically ranges from \u20b930,000 to \u20b91,00,000 (around $400 to $1,300 USD) depending on the clinic, the expertise of the surgeon, the number of grafts required, and the technology used (such as FUE or FUT techniques). It's advisable to consult with a qualified practitioner for a personalized assessment and an accurate quote.",
